    dc:creator "Bauer, Aaron M.; Jackman, Todd R.; Sadlier, Ross A.; Whitaker, Anthony H." ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the giant geckos of New Caledonia (Reptilia: Diplodactylidae: Rhacodactylus)" ;
